      "seed": 552776017,
      "version": 556,
      "versionNonce": 1983068831,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776016579083,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Example Use case:\n \nBasic URL : -\nhttps://www.abc.com/q=chat&c=abc&d=efg&user=s\njhdjshdsjdhjsdh%sdjshjhsj\nConverted to TinyURL :\nhttps://wwwtinyURL.com/abc4545\n\nIf you click the TinyURL it will still redirect to\nthe actual website.\n\nAlways generate a Unique URL \nShort URL -> Long URL -> Website\n\nManage the link analytics => No of views for each\nlink",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Example Use case:\n \nBasic URL : - https://www.abc.com/q=chat&c=abc&d=efg&user=sjhdjshdsjdhjsdh%sdjshjhsj\nConverted to TinyURL : https://wwwtinyURL.com/abc4545\n\nIf you click the TinyURL it will still redirect to the actual website.\n\nAlways generate a Unique URL \nShort URL -> Long URL -> Website\n\nManage the link analytics => No of views for each link",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "rxsUeVACBLoDbSsvJIazY",
      "type": "text",
